We have recommended the Municipality to:
1. Conduct pre-repair and post-repair inspections for the repair and maintenance of motor vehicles and equipment;
2. Submit the complete list of motor vehicles and other transportation equipment with Acknowledgement Receipt for Equipment;
3. Maintain subsidiary ledger for each motor vehicle, transportation equipment and equipment, indicate also the history of repair and attach to the disbursement voucher for succeeding repairs and maintenance.

It is recommended for the municipality to:

Make a request for the write-off of the P2,968,297.82 to be addressed to the Commission Proper;

Intensify collection of the long overdue receivables. Strict collection strategies should be adopted.
